### Create Campaign
POST http://localhost:5000/campaigns
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test Campaign",
    "advertiser": "Test Co",
    "budget": 1000,
    "startDate": "2023-01-01",
    "endDate": "2023-02-01"
}

### List Campaigns
GET http://localhost:5000/campaigns

### Get Campaign Details
# Replace ID with a valid one from the list
GET http://localhost:5000/campaigns/REPLACE_WITH_ID

### Get Campaign Stats
# Replace ID with a valid one
GET http://localhost:5000/campaigns/REPLACE_WITH_ID/stats

### Toggle Status
# Replace ID with a valid one
PATCH http://localhost:5000/campaigns/REPLACE_WITH_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "active"
}
